			Mouse	
			Configure Mouse
			by Guido Schimmels

Changes in release 0.10:

- Added Zero Install interface file for people running developer versions
  (Thomas Leonard).

06-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.9.1)

Modified to support more consistent new naming convention in settings.py and
to perform garbage collection if theme changes (Tony Houghton).

04-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.9.0)

New generic settings.py, compatible with dbus 0.36 bindings (Tony Houghton).

25-April-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Compatible with dbus 0.32 bindings (Tony Houghton).

2-September-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
(Version 0.8.3)

Allow resetting Xcursor theme to "" listet as "No Theme".
Added "Theme Folder" button to conveniently get to "~/.icons".

30-August-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.8.2)

Options for changing Xcursor theme and Xcursor size.

01-August-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.8.1)

Support changing button order for left handed use.
(ROX-Session patch sent to Thomas Leonard)

02-May-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.8)
Created a first, fully functional version.

